                      TO  RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL
               END-IF

      *       명목액기준한도
               MOVE  XBJLTGEX-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM

      *       명목액기준잔액
               MOVE  XBJLTGEX-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL

           ELSE

      *       월말 AND 원화환산잔액> 0
      *        BS기준잔액
               IF ( WK-CHK-DATE = WK-H-O-BASE-YMD  AND
                    WK-H-O-WONC-UTCNG-BAL > 0 )
               THEN
      *             BS기준잔액＝원화환산잔액
                    MOVE  WK-H-O-WONC-UTCNG-BAL
                      TO  RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL
               ELSE
      *             BS기준잔액
                    MOVE  ZERO
                      TO  RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL
               END-IF

      *       명목액기준한도
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM

      *       명목액기준잔액
               MOVE  ZERO
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL
           END-IF
           .
       S3320-BJLTGEX-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

