       S5000-CJIIL09-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    XCJIIL09-CA
                         WK-CHK-DATE

      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD    TO  XCJIIL09-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *   구분코드
