      *   년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD       TO  XCJIIL09-I-YMD
      *   가산월/감산월
           MOVE  CO-CHA-0              TO  XCJIIL09-I-PLS-SBTR-MN

      * 공통 UTILITY CALL
           #DYCALL CJIIL09 YCCOMMON-CA XCJIIL09-CA

      * RETURN 정보 확인
           IF  XCJIIL09-R-STAT = ZEROS
      *        정상처리
               MOVE  XCJIIL09-O-ENMN-BZOPR-YMD
                 TO  WK-CHK-DATE
           ELSE
      *       에러처리
               MOVE  SPACE             TO  WK-CHK-DATE
           END-IF
           .
       S5000-CJIIL09-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
